      "content": "makes sense. but i've noticed that certain politicians or groups use the term \"fake news\" basically every time they get criticized by mainstream media. if it's actually a documented reality of \"information warfare,\" how can you tell the difference between a legitimate disinformation campaign and just a person or outlet being biased or wrong?",
